data.title: Graph
data.description: The graph visualization shows nodes connected by edges and already basic filtering by label, degree and other attributes.

data.title: Text
data.description: The text visualization prints simple unformated text. If an object is passed instead of a string, it is transformed into pretty-printed JSON.

data.title: Line Chart
data.description: The line chart can display multiple lines or points on a x-y axis.

data.title: Bar Chart
data.description: The bar chart shows values of ordinal categories.

data.title: Stacked Area Chart
data.description: The stacked area chart shows multiple values over time stacked on top of each other.
